[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "待たせたな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01366",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "いえ、とんでもないです！　むしろいきなり\n会いに来たのに時間を作っていただいて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01367",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "「九偉人図」集めのほうは、捗ってますか～？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01368",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ、おかげでピルッツァ島でも「九偉人図」を１枚\n見つけることができたわ。でも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01369",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "また九偉人図の手掛かりがなくなっちゃったんすよね。\nそれで何か監察局本部のほうに情報はないかな～って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01370",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "「九偉人図」に関しての新たな情報は今のところない。\n一応、前向きな情報ならあるが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01371",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "んん？　どういうことすか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01372R",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ただ、それより先にこちらの情報を共有してもいいか？\n実はベスティラに九偉人らしき男がやって来た",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01373",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なんですって！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01374",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトがベスティラ王を襲った……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01375",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それで、陛下はご無事なんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01376",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい、お命に別状はありません。\nなんとか一命をとりとめました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01377",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あのとんでもなく強かった王様を倒すとか……\nやっぱり、ヘルトの力は伊達じゃない……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01378",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "まさか、旅先で暴れ始めるなんて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01379",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "自分が「管理」をしようと考えている。\nそんなことを言っていました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01380",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……そっか、そっちの結論に行くんだ。\nとなると、もう放っておくだけで危険だわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01381",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトとは、一度きちんと\n決着を付けないといけないでしょうね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01382",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "で、それはそれとして……\n「九偉人図」について前向きな情報ってのは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01383",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ああ。諸島同盟監察官として正式に\nジョゼ・ダンブロシオに協力を要請できる運びになった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01384",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "あいつの実力は確かだ。加えて、法の下にある我々には\nない灰色の情報網も持っている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01385",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さんと一緒なのはちょっと楽しみですね～。\nいつもどんな風に過ごしているんでしょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01386",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でもその情報網が使えるなら確かにありがたいっすね。\nうちらは正直、手詰まりでしたんで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01387",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "「九偉人図」も残り４枚……数が減るごとに\n見つけづらくなるのはしょうがないけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01388",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "まあ、まだ運びがついただけで、交渉はこれからだ。\nなんとしてでも奴を口説き落とさねば",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01389",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それでしたら……私たちにも手伝わせてください！\nジョゼさんにはぜひ手伝ってほしいですし！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01390",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そうだな、君たちも知った顔だし……\n説得が成功する確率は少しでも上げたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01391",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "んじゃ、全員でジョゼを説得にしゅっぱーつ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01392",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]